Class DoubleLongPair

java.lang.Object
  edu.stanford.math.plex_plus.datastructures.pairs.DoubleLongPair
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<DoubleLongPair>
public class DoubleLongPair
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DoubleLongPair>

This class implements a pair (d, l), where d is a double and l is a long. It implements the Comparable interface with dictionary ordering. Note that any instance of this class is immutable, and implements value semantics.

Author:
Andrew Tausz
